text: Wang Weiyi (born 20 June 1995) is a Chinese female volleyball player. She was part of the China women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2015 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2019 Asian Volleyball Championship. On a club level, she played for Shanghai women's volleyball team. == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese volleyball players
